{"id": 2561, "genre": 1001, "title": "在大城市生活，住处之外你觉得在哪可能更有归属感？", "description": "之前临时借住在朋友一个很多小强的屋子里，我对对面的麦当劳更有归属感。（题图来自：iStock ©️CSA Images )", "record_count": 3004, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181010113732elOqdpaoJL8Fs7cf.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-10-11T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 303360, "content": "厨房", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1447913}, {"id": 303361, "content": "被窝里", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713283}, {"id": 304129, "content": "肯德基", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1313812}, {"id": 303363, "content": "在老家经常逛的一些店，在这里看到了连锁的店铺，感觉我不是一个人在这座城市。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467875}, {"id": 303620, "content": "单位", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1468398}, {"id": 303365, "content": "我家的矿山", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185153}, {"id": 305669, "content": "最喜欢的城市哪里都有归属感", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1469739}, {"id": 305925, "content": "租房吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479346}, {"id": 303366, "content": "朋友开的清水吧台，很少对外开放，下班以后和朋友两个人一起坐在里面，喝着淡酒，聊着最近发生的新鲜事情……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467763}, {"id": 303368, "content": "网吧。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359104}, {"id": 303369, "content": "去过几次的博物馆", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467879}, {"id": 303370, "content": "他家最近的咖啡厅", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467881}, {"id": 303372, "content": "他家最近的咖啡馆\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467881}, {"id": 303373, "content": "就是楼下左拐角杂货店老板，右边文具店老板娘，修车李师傅还有小吃摊师傅，下班回家一一打招呼，阴天提醒你关窗户，收衣服，每天照顾院里的小孩，让他们不要乱跑，日常生活守护神们，没错，就是这块街角的人们！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1102951}, {"id": 303374, "content": "在自己喜欢的城市，哪里都觉得她是我要的", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415034}, {"id": 303375, "content": "也许……有了女朋友之后？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1464959}, {"id": 311311, "content": "IMAX影厅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182031}, {"id": 303888, "content": "下班后自己的沙发里", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433352}, {"id": 303377, "content": "只有学校宿舍", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467903}, {"id": 303378, "content": "没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467906}, {"id": 303890, "content": "街边楼上的有情怀的小清吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1469494}, {"id": 303379, "content": "书店", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1451963}, {"id": 303380, "content": "公司", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1145289}, {"id": 303381, "content": "十点以后的地铁里", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1335631}, {"id": 303382, "content": "银行！VIP室", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020441}, {"id": 303383, "content": "一块触脚可及的足球场⚽️...", "image": "img/option/option/20181011182837L1YrEZMnAHzuwedo.jpg", "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761683}, {"id": 303384, "content": "陌生的地方永远感觉不到归属感", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838273}, {"id": 304664, "content": "除了宿舍的床，还真没有归属感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240486}, {"id": 303385, "content": "各种美食面前🐷", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635296}, {"id": 303386, "content": "朋友家的厨房", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437040}, {"id": 303899, "content": "自己的车子里面？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470069}, {"id": 303388, "content": "公交538路", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466917}, {"id": 303901, "content": "一个可以喝啤酒的阳台。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1308364}, {"id": 303390, "content": "其实在家也没什么归属感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324195}, {"id": 303392, "content": "公交车最后一排", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1422795}, {"id": 303648, "content": "寺庙", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428593}, {"id": 303393, "content": "只有家里的那张床，只有睡觉时钻进被窝里的那一刻才会感觉到归属感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467935}, {"id": 303394, "content": "钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467927}, {"id": 303395, "content": "曾经上过学的教室", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467938}, {"id": 303396, "content": "公交车与小吃店 灵魂的落脚处", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461099}, {"id": 303908, "content": "没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470163}, {"id": 304422, "content": "实验室。旁边没人心里就很宁静。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162492}, {"id": 303399, "content": "找间安静的咖啡厅，静静读一会书", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466651}, {"id": 303400, "content": "坐在公交车上，拖着疲惫，看着窗外的人流，有一种安心", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466913}, {"id": 303401, "content": "这是个好问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665111}, {"id": 303913, "content":